Comment:
 This package repackages the official upstream self-contained Linux x64
 release (Mesen_2.1.1_Linux_x64.zip) — a .NET ahead-of-time-compiled,
 single-file binary. The binary bundles third-party native and managed
 components (Avalonia, SkiaSharp, HarfBuzzSharp, the .NET runtime), each
 distributed under its own permissive licence (predominantly MIT). Mesen
 itself, and this packaging, are licensed under the GNU GPL version 3.

